helpme - self defined help

[ VIM: Show which syntax highlighting current file ]
:setlocal syntax?

[ VIM: Disable visible whitespaces ]
:set nolist

[ VIM: Count lines of source codes ]
find . -name "*" | xargs wc -l

[ VIM: Using vi as a hex editor ]
:%!xxd      - to hex mode
:%!xxd -r   - return to text mode

[ tmux: Basic usage ]
tmux ls
tmux new-session -s SESSION_NAME
tmux attach-session -t SESSION_NAME
<Ctrl+b><d>: Detach session.
<Ctrl+b><">: Split pane vertically.
<Ctrl+b><o>: Next pane.
